Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning there was darkness and then
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}bang giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now see further that we've ever imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "the universe".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那无限的宇宙充满着怪异 暴戾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our infinite universe is brimming with strange, violent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及潜在的生命传输现象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and potentially life-transporting phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下宇宙的门户\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine cosmic portals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里物体会消失 被弹出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where objects could disappear, be ejected
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者泄漏到时空中的一些其它的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or escape to some other place in space or time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是去绝大多数湮没之地的入场券\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are tickets to oblivion for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或者在通过虫洞传送到宇宙的另一部分去时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Either you get shredded in a black hole you get transported
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑洞碾得粉碎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to another part of the universe in a wormhole, or you get
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者被白洞的喷射物所毁灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}obliterated by the gusher of the white hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行去宇宙的弯曲的那头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Blast off to the warp side of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家们为了搜索黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as scientists search for black holes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白洞和虫洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}white holes and wormholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是没有意义的幻想… 还是一个科学事实呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are they frivolous fantasies... or a science fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.00,Default,,0,0,1,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://cmct.cc{\r}
